  "reference_number": "BEL0145",
  "remarks": "\nMikhail KAVALIOU is an involved person under the Belarus (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the basis of the following grounds: KAVALIOU is or has been responsible for, engaging in, providing support for, or promoting: (1) the repression of civil society or democratic opposition in Belarus and (2) actions, policies or activities which undermine democracy or the rule of law in Belarus. \n",
